data.description: Great home that is close to town and schools with solar! This 3 bedroom, 2 bath Broadview Terrace home has a wonderful fenced yard and a relaxing patio area. The interior has a large living area with vaulted ceilings and large bay window, a remodeled kitchen with granite counters, breakfast bar, built-in stainless steel appliances and a dining area with sliding glass door to the back yard. There is a large laundry room with storage/pantry. The guest bedrooms have ceiling fans and carpet flooring and the primary bedroom and main living area have vinyl. The primary bathroom offers a double sink vanity, walk-in closet and privacy toilet with shower. This is a great starter home with elementary, middle and high schools just a few blocks away and minutes to shopping in Oakhurst. Excellent location in town but just a short drive to Yosemite for one of the most beautiful national parks and Bass Lake for fun and fishing! This is a wonderful opportunity so make an appointment today!
